WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: hr

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Prevoditelj: Dunja Vucenovic
Recezent: Predrag Pale

00:00:21.330 --> 00:00:24.330
Ovo označava da se smijem.

00:00:24.330 --> 00:00:27.330
Kao i ovo.

00:00:27.330 --> 00:00:29.330
Ovo predstavlja miša

00:00:29.330 --> 00:00:31.330
mačku.

00:00:32.330 --> 00:00:34.330
Ovo je priča.

00:00:34.330 --> 00:00:37.330
Početak priče, gdje ovo predstavlja momka

00:00:37.330 --> 00:00:42.330
a ovo je konjski rep prolaznice.

00:00:44.330 --> 00:00:47.330
Ovdje se sve događa.

00:00:47.330 --> 00:00:49.330
i kad se događa.

00:00:49.330 --> 00:00:52.330
Ovo je kazeta koju djevojka stavlja u svoj kazetofon.

00:00:52.330 --> 00:00:54.330
To radi svaki dan.

00:00:54.330 --> 00:00:55.330
Ne smatra se staromodnim --

00:00:55.330 --> 00:00:57.330
samo voli da određena muzika zvuči posebno.

00:00:57.330 --> 00:00:59.330
Pogledajte njenu pozu, nevjerojatno.

00:00:59.330 --> 00:01:01.330
To je zato što pleše.

00:01:01.330 --> 00:01:03.330
A on, momak, sve to promatra, razmišljajući,

00:01:03.330 --> 00:01:07.330
"Iskreno, kakve su mi šanse?"

00:01:07.330 --> 00:01:08.330
(Smijeh)

00:01:08.330 --> 00:01:11.330
I mogao bi reći, "O moj Bože!"

00:01:11.330 --> 00:01:13.330
ili "Volim te"

00:01:13.330 --> 00:01:15.330
Glasno se smijem

00:01:15.330 --> 00:01:17.330
Želim te zagrliti.

00:01:17.330 --> 00:01:19.330
Ali on se sjeti nečeg drugog

00:01:19.330 --> 00:01:23.330
Kaže joj, "Rado bih te rukom portretirao na šalicu"

00:01:23.330 --> 00:01:25.330
(Smijeh)

00:01:25.330 --> 00:01:27.330
Staviti raka unutra.

00:01:27.330 --> 00:01:29.330
Dodati vode.

00:01:29.330 --> 00:01:31.330
Sedam različitih soli.

00:01:31.330 --> 00:01:34.330
Misli da je odjednom shvatio pojam stajati čvrsto na tlu

00:01:34.330 --> 00:01:36.330
ali poput poluotoka u oceanu.

00:01:36.330 --> 00:01:42.330
Kaže, "Izgledaš poput sirene, a hodaš kao da plešeš valcer."

00:01:42.330 --> 00:01:46.330
Djevojka ga pita, "Što?"

00:01:47.330 --> 00:01:49.330
Momak odgovori, "Da, znam, znam."

00:01:49.330 --> 00:01:52.330
Mislim da bi mi otkucaji srca mogli biti Morseov kod za neprikladno.

00:01:52.330 --> 00:01:54.330
Bar se tako čini.

00:01:54.330 --> 00:01:58.330
Ponekad sam poput mladog navijača prvog tima -.

00:01:58.330 --> 00:02:03.330
za psovke, neugodne tišine i jednostavne rime.

00:02:03.330 --> 00:02:08.330
Sad, dok pričam s tobom, ne osjećam se poput muškarca.

00:02:08.330 --> 00:02:10.330
Majmun sam,

00:02:10.330 --> 00:02:11.330
(smijeh)

00:02:11.330 --> 00:02:13.330
koji šalje poljubce

00:02:13.330 --> 00:02:15.330
leptiru.

00:02:15.330 --> 00:02:18.330
Al' još uvijek predlažem da se sastanemo.

00:02:18.330 --> 00:02:23.330
Ubrzo, a poslije često.

00:02:23.330 --> 00:02:27.330
Razmišljam o sjeverozapadnom kutu 5. i 42. ulice sutra u podne,

00:02:27.330 --> 00:02:31.330
bit ću tamo dok se ne pojavis, s repom ili bez.

00:02:31.330 --> 00:02:33.330
Strašno, rep sam.

00:02:33.330 --> 00:02:35.330
Ne znam što da ti kažem.

00:02:35.330 --> 00:02:37.330
Imam olovku koju ti mogu posuditi.

00:02:37.330 --> 00:02:40.330
Možeš ju staviti u mobitel."

00:02:40.330 --> 00:02:48.330
Ali djevojka se ne miče, ne smije i ne mršti.

00:02:48.330 --> 00:02:52.330
Samo kaže, "Ne, hvala."

00:02:52.330 --> 00:02:54.330
Znate?

00:02:56.330 --> 00:03:02.330
["ne moram to pisati."]

00:03:02.330 --> 00:03:12.330
(Pljesak)

